    SELECT hadm_id, admittime
    FROM ADMISSIONS
    WHERE subject_id = 18771968
    ORDER BY admittime DESC
    LIMIT 1
),

    SELECT hadm_id
    FROM ADMISSIONS
    WHERE subject_id = 18771968 AND admittime < (SELECT admittime FROM LastAdmission)
    ORDER BY admittime DESC
    LIMIT 1
)
SELECT study_id, image_id
FROM TB_CXR
WHERE hadm_id = (SELECT hadm_id FROM PreviousAdmission) AND subject_id = 18771968
ORDER BY studydatetime DESC
LIMIT 1;
